des:
Zombie who? Maybe you! Are you the one? It's a fun turn-based voice game of discovery to let you know who's a zombie or other critter in disguised sitting on your couch or standing right over there! Or play solo if you're curious if your slowly transforming into a zombie bunny. Alexa will let you know. 

You may not have a magic mirror mirror on a wall, but you and your friends do have magic Alexa Alexa to help you see your goofy inner reflections.

Switch from finding zombies to just about anything. Say "find _____" to switch up what you're looking for and find who's the ________ among your party friends.
